    <abstract>
      <t>The INFO extention method for SIP is introduced in RFC2976 [1], which
is base on RFC2543.  Since RFC2543 is obsoleted by RFC3261 [3], It is
suggested to update RFC2976 to conform to RFC3261.

	 </t>
